data.description: Beautiful updated waterfront home on a quiet established and mature oak tree lined road in Altamonte Springs. Super close to I-4, shopping, dining. Home remodeled & updated in 2008 to include a modern gourmet kitchen, new A/C unit, partial re-plumb, new  paint and flooring. Large upstairs loft with great lake views can be used as an office with built-in bookcases or a 2nd living/ family room.   Gas fireplace in living room with 2 sets of French doors and windows that look out over lake, or relax in the fully screened in patio.  Backyard is fully fenced with mature landscaping to provide your own semi-private oasis. Master bedroom is downstairs, that also overlooks lake with a modern en-suite bathroom and custom closet shelving!  Home is setup for termite bond service and seller is including a home warranty! High efficiency Samsung washer and dryer is also being included!
data.whatILove: Beautiful quiet and small neighborhood that is close to everything.   Home sits on Lake Suzanne with plenty of wildlife watching and a semi-private side and backyard oasis.   Home is partially remodeled to be contemporary with a nice open and airy floorplan with high ceilings, loft overlooking living room and lots of windows and natural light. Feel free to bring your qualify buyer we will be happily to pay your 2.5 % for buyer’s agent !
